{"type": "article", "id": 31552, "title": "把杂乱的电线收进“豌豆荚”里｜这个设计了不起", "description": "我们每天都为你推荐几个最近发现的好设计。", "date": "2016-08-28T23:00:57Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 32091, "name": "fruitsuper design"}, {"id": 32092, "name": "Andreas Kowalewski"}, {"id": 32093, "name": "Caussa"}, {"id": 32094, "name": "Mitz Takahashi"}, {"id": 32095, "name": "Albi Serfaty"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 5, "praise_count": 119, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160828232351N0aKPSoD4eywTBn8.jpg", "contents": "<p>          </p><p>「这个设计了不起」的微信公众号上线啦，直接搜索「BestDesign」或是「Qthings」就可以订阅，关注我们每日发现的新鲜好设计。</p><h3>Kumo chair by Mitz Takahashi</h3><p>劳累了一天之后，回到家中的你是不是恨不得立刻找件舒适的家具开始“瘫”着？如果你对颜值也有一定要求，不妨看看这张叫 Kumo 的躺椅，它是加拿大日裔设计师 <a href=\"http://mitztakahashi.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Mitz Takahashi</a> 的最新作品，名字在日语里意为“云朵”。黑色金属框架所支撑的并不是常见的椅背，而是一条长长的帆布枕头，两端各由一根橡木栓固定，结合处也被巧妙地隐藏在了木栓当中，无缝的设计让它看上去就像是一片被禁锢住的云朵。Kumo 的颜色可以进行定制，如果你感兴趣的话可以通过<a href=\"http://mitztakahashi.com/Kumo-Chair\" rel=\"nofollow\">链接</a>中的邮箱与设计师联系。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160828232658H4LycVneGJIavYjT.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160828232658fY69nOv0E3MFNDpg.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160828232658KhqIxd4GACystFgp.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Strike Up Match Holder+Striker by fruitsuper design</h3><p>什么样的火柴盒会是人们愿意放在桌面上的？西雅图设计工作室 <a href=\"http://www.fruitsuperdesign.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">fruitsuper design</a> 设计的这款 Strike Up 给出了一个有趣的答案。它看上去就像一座黑色的小型火山，放上火柴之后就会形象地展现出熔浆迸发时的场景。由于外壳采用磨砂材质，只要在表面轻松一划就可以点燃，非常实用。这是它的<a href=\"http://www.fruitsuperdesign.com/Strike-Up-Match-HolderStriker-_p_37.html\" rel=\"nofollow\">购买链接</a>，售价为 48 美元。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160828232638bH7OlehNxJ6dVjtf.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201608282326381dK7oBVAZsr8NzcR.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666406\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160828232638FyiXxZONdCT8hWRw.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160828232638RSoimzYCr1BPZX3t.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160828232638BhviPM85WT3b4Kqz.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160828232638hvGlTOdYRu9Bb7ga.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Wedge Table by Andreas Kowalewski</h3><p>来自阿姆斯特丹的设计师 <a href=\"http://andreaskowalewski.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Andreas Kowalewski</a> 最近为德国品牌 Caussa 设计了一款用胶合板组合而成的边桌 Wedge。和其他边桌不同的是，Wedge 的桌腿其实是由三块胶合板穿插而成，Kowalewski 在细致的计算后设计出了这一简洁而且稳定的结构，让它同时可以作为矮凳使用。你可以通过 <a href=\"http://caussa.de/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Caussa</a> 的官网进行购买，售价为 299 和 329 欧元。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201608282326017WvG4Yk5C8tRSQVw.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.709375\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201608282326017MOJmRwbF1HKNq8X.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.710000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160828232601odU4MHG9vBgj82Df.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.645000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160828232602IGwokFj2LrHRcgu6.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.673333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201608282326018yi4lmcgEKsMafGC.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.226667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160828232601wLbx5q3H1WrYRvzJ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.708333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Lucky Lamp by Albi Serfaty</h3><p>艺术家和设计师 Albi Serfaty 在 LED 专家 Michael Zeron 的帮助下打造了一款游离在产品和艺术之间的壁灯 <a href=\"http://aquagallery.com/items/lucky-lamp/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Lucky</a>。激光切割的铝制底座总共容纳了 920 个 LED 灯，外面覆盖着喷洒了聚合物的灯罩，由于采用手工打造，每一个灯罩的造型都是独一无二的。Lucky 不断变化循环的灯光能够呈现出火、土、风、水以及万花筒这五种主题色，还可以根据需要设定颜色的冷暖程度。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201608282325210udLa72AfbElySrH.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.776667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160828232520AxweYs3d97V1pJoP.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.729688\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160828232520hg0tBXzGJlxLaQ42.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.755000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160828232524PXufyUgoiDnH7VGa.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160828232520qINt9LmC7r5028EF.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160828232521uWJeApXK8Hcsf6o7.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Arrangement PEA by Prof. Baek Junghoon et al.</h3><p>你有没有为接线板上杂乱的电源线感到头疼？由韩国的设计团队带来的 Arrangement PEA 是一个可以帮你让电线“眼不见为净”的接线板，并且有着可爱的豌豆荚造型。它的底座部分由硬塑料制成，深绿色的“豆皮”则使用了有延展性的硅料，向上翻起后就可以将不在使用的电线缠绕在里面。它不仅可以帮助人们更好地分辨出电线，也能让环境变得更加整洁。Arrangement PEA 目前还是一款概念设计，此前还获得了 <a href=\"http://www.red-dot.sg/zh/online-exhibition/arrangement-pea/\" rel=\"nofollow\">2015 年红点奖</a>的肯定。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160828232504Y1bc2p0Rvxm37u6s.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667619\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160828232504oXrQBzFiSlLW83g6.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201608282325047qeSmf0gnMuxVdA4.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.619048\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160828232504pvLV0gGjZCeI9Ku6.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Wild Honey by Yinersi Gonzales</h3><p>Wild Honey 是美国设计学生 Yinersi Gonzales 为包装设计课打造的一个概念品牌，小小的玻璃瓶上贴有代表着四种不同口味的标签，同时用来封住瓶盖。标签的一头就像是一勺蜂蜜缓慢地向下流淌时所带出的绵软的印迹，带有一种特别的流动感。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160828232445oOt3r21g87K9RvFe.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.664000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160828232446xBqVJ7s5TwFN4vuC.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160828232446o6gu0ZGE5elApf2T.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.498667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160828232446u9eQaztb7J6qCU45.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>"}